<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xml:id="pit_vertica_recovery"><title>&kw-hos-tm; &kw-hos-version-50;: Point-in-Time Vertica Recovery</title>
    <formalpara><title>Recovering the Vertica Database</title><para><para>In order to recover your Vertica databases, run the following playbook:</para></para>
<screen>cd ~/scratch/ansible/next/hos/ansible
ansible-playbook -i hosts/verb_hosts monasca-vertica-recovery.yml</screen>
<para><para>or if you have encryption enabled, use:</para></para>
<screen>ansible-playbook -i hosts/verb_hosts monasca-vertica-recovery.yml --ask-vault-pass</screen>
</formalpara>
